column11: A powerful and majestic Pokémon with incredible strength. Its vines can grab and restrain opponents.
A fierce and agile Pokémon with quick reflexes. It can generate intense heat using its body to attack opponents.
A small but powerful Pokémon that uses its razor-sharp claws and strong legs to take down opponents. Its vines are also used for defense.
A matured form of Bulbasaur, with a more developed sense of battle strategy. Its vines have become thicker and stronger, allowing it to bind opponents even tighter.
A small, lizard-like Pokémon with flames on its tail. It can breathe fire and has high attack power.
A turtle-like Pokémon that can shoot water from its shell. It is very strong in battle.
A large, insect-like Pokémon with powerful legs. Its vines are also used for defense.
A massive sea creature with a powerful tail. It can swim at incredible speeds and has great strength.
A water-type Pokémon that can evolve into Blastoise. It has a large shell on its back and can shoot powerful water attacks.
A fire-type Pokémon that can fly using its large wings. It is known for its immense strength and fierce battles.
